cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE

This paper deals with natural language understanding tasks, specifically in the context of cross-lingual transfer learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses meta-learning techniques, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves training models on multiple languages, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) if the models involve image processing. Finally, the paper uses neural networks, which could also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
